{"id": "174115", "revid": "55511441", "url": "https://wowpedia.fandom.com/wiki?curid=174115", "title": "Grimclaw", "text": "Grimclaw is a &lt;a href=\"polar%20bear\"&gt;polar bear&lt;/a&gt; found in &lt;a href=\"Darkshore\"&gt;Darkshore&lt;/a&gt;. To be precise, he is located by the main north-south road, just a short distance south of the fork where you walk off to the &lt;a href=\"Grove%20of%20the%20Ancients\"&gt;Grove of the Ancients&lt;/a&gt;, on the left hand side of the road if you are facing south.\nHe plays a part in &lt;a href=\"A%20Lost%20Master%20%282%29\"&gt;A Lost Master (2)&lt;/a&gt; by pointing in the direction towards his master, &lt;a href=\"Volcor\"&gt;Volcor&lt;/a&gt;, when you wave at him (by typing \"/wave\" when he looks at you). He is introduced to you in the quest &lt;a href=\"How%20Big%20a%20Threat%3F%20%282%29\"&gt;How Big a Threat? (2)&lt;/a&gt; where he signals Volcor's danger to &lt;a href=\"Terenthis\"&gt;Terenthis&lt;/a&gt;.\nCataclysm.\nIn \"\", Grimclaw was sent by &lt;a href=\"Volcor\"&gt;Volcor&lt;/a&gt; ahead of &lt;a href=\"Ruins%20of%20Auberdine\"&gt;Auberdine's destruction&lt;/a&gt; and is badly injured by poachers. &lt;a href=\"Keeper%20Karithus\"&gt;Keeper Karithus&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Seraphine\"&gt;Seraphine&lt;/a&gt; watch over the injured bear and task you with seeking out various remedies, before he can be safely moved to &lt;a href=\"Lor%27danel\"&gt;Lor'danel&lt;/a&gt;. After receiving treatment phased content shows Grimclaw in Lor'danel, where you learn that Volcor has just died from his injuries.\nIn a later phase, Grimclaw has decided to associate himself as the companion of &lt;a href=\"Cerellean%20Whiteclaw\"&gt;Cerellean Whiteclaw&lt;/a&gt;, who finds more comfort with the bear's presence than he would have first thought.\nDragonflight.\nIn , Grimclaw can now be found swimming beside the docks at Belanaar, &lt;a href=\"Amirdrassil\"&gt;Amirdrassil&lt;/a&gt;, right beside Cerellean Whiteclaw."}
