esecration&lt;/a&gt;! The time has come for me to personally complete this task. Before my power, all will fall! All will be tainted with the infernal blessings of &lt;a href=\"Destruction\"&gt;Destruction&lt;/a&gt;! Ye have defeated my minions! Damn ye! But can you defeat me?\""}
