{"id": "482905", "revid": "40389549", "url": "https://wowpedia.fandom.com/wiki?curid=482905", "title": "Azuregale Bay", "text": "Azuregale Bay is a large body of water located in the east of &lt;a href=\"Suramar\"&gt;Suramar&lt;/a&gt;. It is notably one of the largest bays on the &lt;a href=\"Broken%20Isles\"&gt;Broken Isles&lt;/a&gt;, opening out into the &lt;a href=\"Great%20Sea\"&gt;Great Sea&lt;/a&gt; towards the &lt;a href=\"Broken%20Shore\"&gt;Broken Shore&lt;/a&gt;. The &lt;a href=\"Trenchwalker\"&gt;Trenchwalker&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"sea%20giant\"&gt;sea giant&lt;/a&gt;s make this bay their home.\nThe bay is primarily inhabited by &lt;a href=\"hammerhead%20shark\"&gt;hammerhead shark&lt;/a&gt;s and contains three small islands, which are themselves home to the &lt;a href=\"Sashj%27tar%20Ruins\"&gt;Sashj'tar Ruins&lt;/a&gt;. The &lt;a href=\"vrykul\"&gt;vrykul&lt;/a&gt; village of &lt;a href=\"Jandvik\"&gt;Jandvik&lt;/a&gt; is situated along the bay's coastline. In recent times, the bay has been occupied by the &lt;a href=\"Sashj%27tar\"&gt;Sashj'tar&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"naga\"&gt;naga&lt;/a&gt;, who have come into conflict with the nearby vrykul, and who have subsequently established themselves on the bay's seafloor and islands. A damaged &lt;a href=\"ley%20line\"&gt;ley line&lt;/a&gt; is found underwater between &lt;a href=\"Jandvik\"&gt;Jandvik&lt;/a&gt; and the southern small isles.\nSpeculation.\nAzuregale Bay may have been the &lt;a href=\"Stormreaver%20Wreckage\"&gt;Stormreaver Wreckage&lt;/a&gt; (from \"\") due to the number of crashed ships present, as well as its proximity to the &lt;a href=\"Tomb%20of%20Sargeras\"&gt;Tomb of Sargeras&lt;/a&gt;."}
