{"id": "334546", "revid": "3154973", "url": "https://wowpedia.fandom.com/wiki?curid=334546", "title": "Huo, the Spirit of Fire", "text": "Objectives.\nReignite &lt;a href=\"Huo\"&gt;Huo&lt;/a&gt;, the spirit of flame.\nDescription.\nYou are worthy of passing, &lt;class&gt;.\nHuo, the spirit of fire rests in the chamber beyond. Let him feast upon the kindling you've gathered, and use the wind to fan his flames. Doing so should endear you to him. Once he is ignited, if he is willing, lead him to the &lt;a href=\"Temple%20of%20Five%20Dawns\"&gt;Temple of Five Dawns&lt;/a&gt;, the building standing high in the center of the island.\nRewards.\nYou will receive: \nProgress.\n&lt;Huo rests quietly within the pool.&gt;\nCompletion.\n&lt;Through the glare, it looks like Huo is smiling. He seems to have warmed up to you.&gt;\nNotes.\nHead up the hill behind Li Fei and approach Huo, the ancient spirit of fire. Use the provided quest item, &lt;a href=\"Huo%27s%20Offerings\"&gt;Huo's Offerings&lt;/a&gt; to continue. Huo will get noticeably bigger and wake up."}
{"id": "345761", "revid": "42014766", "url": "https://wowpedia.fandom.com/wiki?curid=345761", "title": "Huo-Shuang", "text": "Huo-Shuang is a &lt;a href=\"mogu\"&gt;mogu&lt;/a&gt; located in the &lt;a href=\"Hall%20of%20the%20Serpent\"&gt;Hall of the Serpent&lt;/a&gt; in the &lt;a href=\"Vale%20of%20Eternal%20Blossoms\"&gt;Vale of Eternal Blossoms&lt;/a&gt;.\nCriteria of.\nKilling Huo-Shang is part of the achievement &lt;a href=\"One%20Many%20Army\"&gt;One Many Army&lt;/a&gt;.\nNotes.\nHuo-Shuang stands in front of the Freezing Water pool at the start of the fight. On aggro he will Double Shot until it's time to cast Flaming Arrow, which is announced by a boss-emote:\nGet in the pool after he starts the cast, let the arrow \"hit\" for no damage, then get out of the pool before the next 30,000 Frost tick. He will then jump to a corner and keep Double-Shotting until he casts Frozen Arrow, which is announced by a boss emote as well. Find the Smoldering Ruin patch on the ground and get in it when the boss emote goes off. Repeat until dead."}
