{"id": "91901", "revid": "22514", "url": "https://wowpedia.fandom.com/wiki?curid=91901", "title": "Crystal of Zin-Malor", "text": "The Crystal of Zin-Malor is a powerful relic that can contain and control strong &lt;a href=\"arcane\"&gt;arcane&lt;/a&gt; forces. Its bearer becomes capable of incredible arcane power, but only if truly worthy.\nHistory.\nThe crystal originally resided at the &lt;a href=\"Temple%20of%20Zin-Malor\"&gt;Temple of Zin-Malor&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a href=\"Azshara\"&gt;Azshara&lt;/a&gt;, but at some point it was stolen by the &lt;a href=\"Highborne\"&gt;Highborne&lt;/a&gt; from the city of &lt;a href=\"Ruins%20of%20Kel%27Theril\"&gt;Kel'Theril&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a href=\"Winterspring\"&gt;Winterspring&lt;/a&gt;. Its ability to control the arcane was too tempting, and when it was toyed with, its shattering cursed the Highborne. Kel'Theril suffered until the &lt;a href=\"Great%20Sundering\"&gt;Great Sundering&lt;/a&gt; destroyed it for good, and now the dead wander the ruins as ghosts.\nOne hundred years ago, a group of &lt;a href=\"high%20elf\"&gt;high elves&lt;/a&gt; led by &lt;a href=\"Archmage%20Maenius\"&gt;Archmage Maenius&lt;/a&gt; came from &lt;a href=\"Quel%27Thalas\"&gt;Quel'Thalas&lt;/a&gt; to Winterspring in search of the crystal. They found its shards, but like the Highborne of millennia before they too ended up as ghosts wandering the ruins. Decades years later, &lt;a href=\"Aurora%20Skycaller\"&gt;Aurora Skycaller&lt;/a&gt; managed to forge the relic's shattered pieces together with the help of an &lt;a href=\"adventurer\"&gt;adventurer&lt;/a&gt;. It was then brought to &lt;a href=\"Darnassus\"&gt;Darnassus&lt;/a&gt; and given to one who would not abuse its power, &lt;a href=\"Fandral%20Staghelm\"&gt;Archdruid Fandral Staghelm&lt;/a&gt;.\nSeveral years later the crystal returned to Winterspring by means unknown and was one of the magical treasures held by &lt;a href=\"Umbranse%20the%20Spiritspeaker\"&gt;Umbranse the Spiritspeaker&lt;/a&gt;. A third group of elves, this time &lt;a href=\"blood%20elf\"&gt;blood elves&lt;/a&gt;, were turned into &lt;a href=\"wretched\"&gt;wretched&lt;/a&gt; by its power. One year after they became wretched Umbranse was slain by an &lt;a href=\"adventurer\"&gt;adventurer&lt;/a&gt;, but the crystal was not recovered. Its current location remains unknown.\nSource.\nObtained during &lt;a href=\"The%20Crystal%20of%20Zin-Malor\"&gt;The Crystal of Zin-Malor&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a href=\"Winterspring\"&gt;Winterspring&lt;/a&gt;, after gathering a number of items from across the world."}
