t;a href=\"Hurricane\"&gt;Hurricane&lt;/a&gt;, etc.). Click the circle to have the cub play with the toy.\nThe &lt;a href=\"Hidden%20Grove\"&gt;Hidden Grove&lt;/a&gt; can be found at the north end of Winterspring, due north of Everlook, and is labeled on the game map. &lt;a href=\"Owl%20Wing%20Thicket\"&gt;Owl Wing Thicket&lt;/a&gt; is at the south end of Winterspring, directly northeast of &lt;a href=\"Frostwhisper%20Gorge\"&gt;Frostwhisper Gorge&lt;/a&gt;."}
